related_questions.question: What is a good SEO Visibility score?
related_questions.snippet: You're looking to get around 35% - 45%, as this is generally the average click through rate of a URL in the top position in the search results. Can I expect to get 100% Search Visibility? No, a Search Visibility score of 100% means you own all of the ranking positions for your keywords.

answer_box.title: What is the SEO Score? – Siteimprove Help Center
answer_box.snippet: The SEO Score is a measure of how well the user-facing and technical aspects of your site contribute to search engine optimization, and ultimately, higher rankings and organic traffic.
